name: Coby Shell
coverLetter: Hi, my name is Coby Shell. Its my dream to become apart of the industry and helping it grow. I have some experience. I can trim 2 pounds a day. I am a hard worker and will get the job done. I applied for my O.L.C.C, I passed the test. I am waiting for my application to be viewed. I'm from Utah. I love the outdoors. I moved to Medford this month. I have my own vehicle. I get along with everyone. Thank you for your time.  You can call me at 801-860-7022
